title: Alyvisun 4Pcs Sink Cleaning Brush, Flexible Unblocker Brushes Drain Dredge Tool Snake for Kitchen Bathroom Drain and Pipe Overflow, 45cm
features: 4PCS Easily Unblock Drains: Our Drain unblocker brush easily clears blocked pipes. With a rotating design, it easily grabs trash, hair, and other dirt from the pipes.
Flexible Enough to Clean Pipes: The Sink cleaning brush is flexible enough to be pre-bent to fit the curves of the pipes, allowing easy access to hard-to-reach spaces to clear out the debris inside.
Quickly Grabs Trash: Simply insert the Drain unblocker brush into the blocked pipe, slowly rotate the brush, and then remove and clean the brush.
Premium Quality Construction: The 4pcs Drain brush is made of PP plastic, nylon bristles, and iron. The 45cm Drain Brush is long enough to reach deep into the pipes, easily unblocking them.
Widely Applicable: The Drain unblocker brush is ideal for cleaning sinks, drains, bathrooms, and kitchen drain holes. It helps to prevent blockages and keep the drains clean.
description: Prevent Blockages, Unblock Pipes! Flexible for Hard-to-Reach Spaces: The Drain Unblocker Brush is flexible enough to easily fit the curves of the pipes when pre-bent. Making it possible to enter hard-to-reach spaces and clear debris. Hole Design for Hanging: The Sink Unblocker Brush can be hung anywhere for convenient storage. Spiral Design Easily Grabs Trash: It can help you easily clean hair and dirt.
